    <h1 class="title">Technology and Child Development: Evidence from the One Laptop per Child Program</h1>
    <ul class="attribution">
            <li class='author' style='margin-bottom:0.5em; '>
         Julian Cristia    </li>
    <li class='author' style='margin-bottom:0.5em; '>
         Pablo Ibarrarán    </li>
    <li class='author' style='margin-bottom:0.5em; '>
